Loyalty Filters

Here are some examples of common loyalty use cases.

Reward Recent Loyalty Program Individuals

Find individuals who recently joined your loyalty program and offer special rewards to retain them.

This filter finds individuals who joined your loyalty program in the last 5 months.

EXAMPLE
Loyalty Program Member | Count | At Least | 1
Enrollment Date | Last Number of Months | 5

This filter finds individuals who joined your loyalty program in the last 5 months and have greater than $200 in Grand Total Amount.

EXAMPLE
Loyalty Program Member | Count | At Least | 1
Enrollment Date | Last Number of Months | 5

AND

Sales Order | Count | At Least | 1
Grand Total Amount | Is Greater Than | 200

Offer Special Discounts to High Status Loyalty Members

This filter finds individuals whose loyalty tier is gold or higher.

EXAMPLE
Loyalty Member Tier | Count | At Least | 1
Tier Name | Is In | Gold, Platinum, Diamond

Find Individuals with Member Points

This filter finds individuals with a point balance greater than 1,000.

EXAMPLE
Loyalty Members Currency | SUM | Point Balance | Is Greater Than | 1000
Points Balance | Is Greater Than | 0

Find Individuals with Silver Status and Member Points

This filter finds individuals with a silver tier status with more than 2,000 points.

EXAMPLE
Loyalty Member Tier | Count | At Least | 1
Tier Name | Is Equal To | Silver

AND

Loyalty Members Currency | SUM | Point Balance | Is Greater Than | 2000
Points Balance | Is Greater Than | 0

Identify Loyalty Members with Gold or Higher Status and High Engagement

This filter finds members who opened or clicked at least 10 emails in the last 2 months.

EXAMPLE
Email Engagement | Count | At Least | 10
Engagement Channel Action | Is In | Click, Open
AND
Engagement Date Time | Last Number Of Months | 2

AND

Loyalty Member Tier | Count | At Least | 1
Tier Name | Is In | Gold, Platinum, Diamond

Find Individuals with More Than 5 Transactions in the Last Year

This filter finds individuals who made more than 5 transactions in the last year.

EXAMPLE
Loyalty Transaction Journal | Count | At Least | 5
Transaction Amount | Is Greater Than | 0
AND
Activity Date | This Year

Find Members That Made Single Transactions Larger Than $1,000

This filter finds members who made single transactions larger than $1,000.

EXAMPLE
Loyalty Transaction Journal | Count | At Least | 1
Transaction Amount | Is Greater Than | 1000

Find Members with Vouchers

This filter finds members who have used a voucher in the last 30 days.

EXAMPLE
Voucher | Count | At Least | 1
Discount Percentage | Is Greater Than| 10
AND
Used Date | Last Number of Days | 30

Find Members with a Voucher Expires Soon

This filter finds members who have a voucher expiring in the next 7 days.

EXAMPLE
Voucher | Count | At Least | 1
Expiration Date | Next Number of Days | 7

Remind Members That Vouchers Are Usable Soon

This filter finds members who have a voucher with an effective date in the next 5 days.

EXAMPLE
Voucher | Count | At Least | 1
Effective Date | Next Number of Days | 5
